	<h2>
			Jango: Ministros se reúnem com população de São Borja/RS		</h2>








        <div style="clear:both;"></div>
        <div class="itp-share">

                	<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/outros-destaques/380-jango-ministros-se-reunem-com-populacao-de-sao-borja-rs.html" data-text="Jango: Ministros se re&uacute;nem com popula&ccedil;&atilde;o de S&atilde;o Borja/RS" data-via="" data-lang="pt" data-size="small" data-related="" data-hashtags="" data-count="none"><img src="file://///mecsrv01/portalmec_dev/www/cnv/site/templates/cnv/images/btn_twitter.png" />Tweet</a><div class="itp-share-fbl">
